{
  "stem": "17626.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 127.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And inside that courtyard, there were all sorts of apartment buildings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The bombing started and I do remember-- I don't remember the danger of it, but I do remember then comfort of it and being in my mother's arms.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the bombs started to fall and the buildings started to collapse.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the police would not let people out of the gates because there were fires, there were sirens, there were horses, there were fire brigades.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Those were the days of the horse and buggy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So with the pressure, I suppose, people, people just broke out of the gates and started running.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Mother carrying me ran a whole day and into the night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was quite late at night with running.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She-- I don't know how she encountered one of her friends, who rescued us and took us into a basement.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the very first day of bombing of Warsaw, September 1.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was within Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You-- masses were running.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were running in one direction and encountered other people running towards them who stopped them and said, don't run any further because such and such a street is burning.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you make another turn and other people keep-- come running saying, don't go any further, we were just there, this street is burning.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was chaotic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It must have been something incredible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- it's like a dream.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I cannot tell you exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I wish Mom were here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She would describe it very, very eloquently.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The next morning, everybody congregated in their own homes to see who, what how survived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because in this rush and panic, my father, my uncle, my grandmother, and mother all dispersed in different directions.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the morning, my mother tried to make her way.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
